title: Possible daylight sighting while riding a dirt bike outside Poinciana
observed: I saw a large two legged figure walk left to right across the road and a car was headed in its direction.  It doubled back and jumped a fence that was there.  I sped to where it was and there was a field it would have had to cross but nothing was there.  Amazing to see but none of my friends believe.
location_details: Call me I'll tell you everything
